---
title: Indian Pumpkin & Coconut Dhal with Coriander Flatbreads
description: Dhal is the ultimate bowl of goodness – rich in protein, a good source of fibre and full of aromatic flavours. The coconut
cream balances the spices to create a meal that's both delectable and nourishing.
